      <note>
	<para>
The application is notified about when a message's status changes by
by invoking the
<function>messageChanged</function> callback method of the currently
opened folder's
<structname>mail::folderCallback</structname> object.
Depending on the mail server, the
<function>messageChanged</function> method may be
invoked as part of processing this request,
or some time later after this request is completed,
and <parameter>callback</parameter>'s <function>success</function>
method was invoked.</para>
      </note>
